# Dashes / myślniki

Do **not** use the em dash (`—`, U+2014) anywhere: UI copy, comments, docs, commit messages, or chat replies for this project.

Use a classic hyphen-minus (`-`) instead.

```text
❌ Odpowiemy w 1 dzień roboczy — szczegóły w salonie.
✅ Odpowiemy w 1 dzień roboczy - szczegóły w salonie.

❌ Layout — outside Tailwind's default spacing scale
✅ Layout - outside Tailwind's default spacing scale
```

Also avoid copying em dashes from prototypes; normalize them to `-` when porting content.
